'''奧德堡'''（{{lang-en|Aldeburgh}}，{{IPA-en|ˈɔːldbrə}}），或譯'''奧爾德堡'''，位於北海沿岸，是[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[薩福克郡|薩福克郡]]的濱海城鎮。{{le|奧德堡音樂節|Aldeburgh Festival}}是享譽英國的音樂盛典<ref name=atc>[http://www.aldeburghtowncouncil.co.uk/index.php?pid=1 Aldeburgh Town Council] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aldeburghtowncouncil.co.uk/index.php?pid=1 |date=20160510125803 }}. Retrieved 2016-01-09.</ref>，當地的著名旅遊景點有藍旗海灘<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2002/feb/10/foodanddrink.features14 | work=The Guardian | location=London | title=Top 10 chip shops | first=Gavin | last=Newsham | date=2002-02-10 | accessdate=2010-04-23 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100414023640/http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2002/feb/10/foodanddrink.features14 | archivedate=2010-04-14 | deadurl=no }}</ref>。

